AGENT 4: ATTESTATION AGENT
================================================================================

PURPOSE
-------
Aggregates all agent outputs into signed attestation payload with AI-generated
professional summary for human readability.

WHAT IT DOES
------------
- Collects outputs from all previous agents
- Uses LLM to generate professional creditworthiness summary
- Packages data into attestation payload
- Saves to Supabase database
- Returns attestation hash for on-chain reference

WORKFLOW
--------
1. Receive complete assessment state from Fraud Agent
2. Build attestation summary prompt
3. Invoke Groq LLM for professional summary generation
4. Parse summary from LLM response
5. Aggregate all data into attestation_payload dict
6. Call save_attestation() to persist in Supabase
7. Generate stub transaction hash (until contracts deployed)
8. Return attestation_hash, tx_hash, summary

OUTPUTS
-------
- attestation_hash: str (Supabase URL)
- tx_hash: str (stub until contract integration)
- attestation_summary: str (AI-generated summary)

