- credit_score: integer
- risk_tier: text
- default_prob_30d: float
- sub_scores: jsonb
- shap_breakdown: jsonb
- fraud_score: float
- fraud_flags: jsonb
- tx_hash: text
- attestation_hash: text
- loan_offers: jsonb
- created_at: timestamptz

FUNCTIONS
---------
- save_attestation(payload): Insert and return URL
- get_assessment(wallet_address): Fetch most recent record


